## Bug Description

After running the onboard/wizard setup, `gateway.controlUi.allowInsecureAuth` remains set to `true` in `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`. This is a security risk for production deployments.

## Environment

- OpenClaw version: 2026.5.3
- macOS: 26.4.1 (arm64)
- Node: 22.22.2

## Current Configuration

```json
{
  "gateway": {
    "controlUi": {
      "allowInsecureAuth": true
    }
  }
}
```

## Expected Behavior

The `allowInsecureAuth` flag should default to `false` after initial...
